Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.66,0:00:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Burger Queen  给你买好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:24.45,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}注： \N 恶搞的汉堡王<Burger King>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.69,0:00:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.41,0:00:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.37,0:00:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以告诉我了吗  这伤是怎么弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.91,0:00:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还真让人意外
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.91,0:00:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为在E潘多拉研究所没法医治
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.98,0:00:53.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然就遣送回了West·Genetics
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:01:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊莉沙白·梅布利是预料到了这点…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.80,0:01:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到外面去冷静一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.61,0:01:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.78,0:01:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也多亏这样  才很难得的能和莎缇拉学姐独处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.53,0:01:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.75,0:01:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些难为情啊  好久都没这样独处过了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.83,0:01:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独…处…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.60,0:01:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.84,0:01:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…  没… 没什么…
