Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:58.90,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}只有守护着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:04.45,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}才懂得憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:09.29,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}拥抱无名的悸动  只是脆弱的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.36,0:03:12.55,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}最终只能轰然溃去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:19.70,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}内心隐藏着野性的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:25.21,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}争斗惨剧  非己所望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:31.69,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}只见希望之星已陨落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:34.60,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}悲惨的宿命在呐喊着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:39.99,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}「撕碎我吧  可爱的人儿」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.02,0:03:42.47,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}「快去攫取  那熹微的梦」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:45.07,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}然而呼喊只是梦幻泡影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:48.46,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}光明与祈祷变成了背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:53.07,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}只能接受那无情的裁罚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:56.32,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}笑靨俱往矣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.37,0:04:02.91,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}唯有迷惘在晨曦
